data.description: One Bedroom/One-and One-Half Bath true Timber Loft Condominium at South Loop's Prairie District Lofts. One of only Five Units in the complex that offer east facing duplex living with A PRIVATE Attached heated garage. Seller will pay for regular assessments through 2023 at closing! Other units have access to outdoor rental parking only.  This unit has exposed brick with an oversized mantel and gas fireplace, hardwood floors and timber ceilings provide a cozy and warm environment!!! The first floor living space is ideal for entertaining with an adjacent area ideal for a home office or at-home working nook.  Sliding glass doors lead to a Juliette balcony for great natural light and fresh air. The updated kitchen features granite counters with a breakfast bar, stainless steel appliances and newer full-size in-unit laundry and very convenient half bath/powder room. The second-floor primary bedroom has an en suite bathroom and professionally organized walk-in closet. Both bathrooms have updated granite vanities.  There are additional storage built-ins in the heated garage as well as a storage cage. The building amenities consist of a fitness center, onsite manager/engineer, common roof deck with grills and lake views.  This Unit is in close proximity and walking distance to all lakefront/beachfront amenities, CTA Bus and Rail Lines, Millenium Park/Grant Park, Soldier Field, Northerly Island, The Museum Campus, McCormick Place, Spoke & Bird, multiple bike/running paths, Marianos and a very popular dog park at your doorstep. Monthly Assessment includes TV/Internet package. Investor friendly!!  Listing Broker's Preferred Lender can provide info on $10K Forgivable Closing Cost Grant!!!  Conditions Apply!!  See Broker Remarks!!!
